{"tid":1671000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友對我做咗啲不能夠原諒既事 我應唔應該原諒佢好","createTime":"2019-10-23T08:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:33:00.000Z","uid":113368,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6c849c03bf89174e3c5a9406d99430ea72a2f808","tid":1671000,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"4個月前，因為唔中意男朋友返大陸。<br />\n好聲好氣叫佢唔好返啦，我唔想你返呀。<br />\n男朋友就意見接受，態度照舊。<br />\n好聲好氣你唔彩我，咁我試下發脾氣啦，睇下你會唔會重視我地既關係而改變初衷啦。<br />\n點知適得其反，仲要被家暴添😥<br />\n啲朋友幫我，你就Block左人地，被消失。<br />\n之後家暴越黎越嚴重，當對男朋友死晒心，決定左分手之後你先同我講你剪左張回鄉咭喇。<br />\n唔再返大陸喇。<br />\n但對家暴一事，隻字不提。<br />\n被Block既朋友，又未出現返。<br />\n<br />\n咁點同你復合，做返以前嗰對恩愛既情侶🤷&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"9c8bc8af361ad5c77eaa50d4e487314803ae185b","tid":1671000,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"應唔應該原諒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140bf1292fff596075c789e199b0ad0a12a3700e","tid":1671000,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"佢搞到我朋友都冇埋"},{"pid":"3fb098bce2f12d5d30f5f795693f71d70572b545","tid":1671000,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e303241c0b16f3d4c2004539fe0cf020ae1515dd","tid":1671000,"uid":114148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"有一就有二 問廢話？"},{"pid":"8d43332f97aeaabbb98e0df42e72d2b9fc96dbf6","tid":1671000,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:38:03.000Z","msg":"[極度緊急]急急急，英國領事館外面急要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e363581ac6f1797c43334f02dcfa0653ffffc1f","tid":1671000,"uid":328114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:38:31.000Z",